Package org.apache.logging.log4j.plugins.di.resolver

@Export @Version("1.0.0") @NullMarked package org.apache.logging.log4j.plugins.di.resolver
Factory resolvers are strategies for creating instances matching supported keys from existing instance factories. Resolvers should be ConfigurableInstanceFactory.registerFactoryResolver(org.apache.logging.log4j.plugins.di.spi.FactoryResolver) registered} via a ConfigurableInstanceFactoryPostProcessor service.
